query: SELECT MIN(chn.name) AS voiced_char, MIN(n.name) AS voicing_actress, MIN(t.title) AS voiced_animation FROM aka_name AS an, complete_cast AS cc, comp_cast_type AS cct1, comp_cast_type AS cct2, char_name AS chn, cast_info AS ci, company_name AS cn, info_type AS it, info_type AS it3, keyword AS k, movie_companies AS mc, movie_info AS mi, movie_keyword AS mk, name AS n, person_info AS pi, role_type AS rt, title AS t WHERE t.id = mi.movie_id AND t.id = mc.movie_id AND t.id = ci.movie_id AND t.id = mk.movie_id AND t.id = cc.movie_id AND mc.movie_id = ci.movie_id AND mc.movie_id = mi.movie_id AND mc.movie_id = mk.movie_id AND mc.movie_id = cc.movie_id AND mi.movie_id = ci.movie_id AND mi.movie_id = mk.movie_id AND mi.movie_id = cc.movie_id AND ci.movie_id = mk.movie_id AND ci.movie_id = cc.movie_id AND mk.movie_id = cc.movie_id AND cn.id = mc.company_id AND it.id = mi.info_type_id AND n.id = ci.person_id AND rt.id = ci.role_id AND n.id = an.person_id AND ci.person_id = an.person_id AND chn.id = ci.person_role_id AND n.id = pi.person_id AND ci.person_id = pi.person_id AND it3.id = pi.info_type_id AND k.id = mk.keyword_id AND cct1.id = cc.subject_id AND cct2.id = cc.status_id AND mi.info in ('Chechen','Kalmyk-Oirat','Rotuman','German','Filipino','Vietnamese') AND it.info not in ('other works','admissions','LD master format','LD review','LD video noise','LD language','other literature','keywords','LD original title','alternate versions','filming dates','LD spaciality') AND it3.info not in ('LD original title','LD number of chapter stops','LD official retail price','LD audio noise','LD disc size','death date','LD video standard','admissions','locations','LD analog right','LD subtitles','adaption','LD label','LD additional information','LD review','LD quality program','LD release date') AND (n.name like '%h%') AND n.gender in ('f') AND cct1.kind in ('cast','complete','crew') AND (cn.name like '%Sony Pictures Entertainment%' OR cn.name like '%Pixar Animation Studios%') AND cn.country_code in ('bd','so','tt','ci','hn') AND (an.name like '%h%' OR an.name like '%i%' OR an.name like '%O%' OR an.name like '%r%' OR an.name like '%R%') AND (rt.role like '%Emily Weber%') AND (k.keyword like '%survival%' OR k.keyword like '%identity%') AND (mc.note like '%Italy%' OR mc.note like '%Germany%') AND t.production_year > 1990 AND t.production_year < 1997 AND cct2.kind in ('crew','cast')
